channel.title: New Client wont run
channel.description:
Im having issues with this new server my friend gave me , it will compile and say "Note: Java\client.java uses unchecked or unsafe operations." and "Note : Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details."
[url=http://pastebin.com/Ja7BGDGR]build.bat - Pastebin.com[/url]
I know these are not errors only notes. Further more when trying to run the Run(64-bit).bat and the Runcmd.bat it will show "Error: could not find or load main class Jframe"
[url=http://pastebin.com/NvMPhZZD]Run (64-bit).bat - Pastebin.com[/url] [url=http://pastebin.com/HGsrWNXr]Run Cmd.bat - Pastebin.com[/url]
[url=http://pastebin.com/2F7Hym9L]Jframe.java - Pastebin.com[/url]
The weird thing about it is when i try to run the RunJVM Error.bat and Run Wind7 i get "Error: Could not find or load main class Gui".
[url=http://pastebin.com/hvmNnUQV]Run JVM Error.bat - Pastebin.com[/url] [url=http://pastebin.com/wKHWrkW6]Run Wind7.bat - Pastebin.com[/url]
I'm sorry if i'm posting this in the wrong area or seem very dumb im trying to learn the basics and build my way up from there.

item.title: New Client wont run
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

In directory /Class/ the file Jframe.class isn’t being found. Perhaps you typed it wrong (it’s case-sensitive, so change it to something like JFrame assuming it exists).
